text.tspan: Laser eyes: convert 1 Plant to Fire
Eyes: Face player with the most stone
A: Mine the highest 2 mountain squares, adding health to Body for each Stone
B: Deal damage to players equal to the damage taken to the Head
C: Deal damage to players equal to the damage taken to Body
Rock throw: Player takes 1 damage per
Slam: Player loses 2 resources from their spell
Eyes: Face player with lowest HP
